main.name: HCONRES75
main.longTitle: CONCURRENT RESOLUTION Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3055.
main.enactingFormula: Resolved by the House of Representatives (the Senate concurring),

section.chapeau: That, in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3055, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall make the following corrections:

paragraph.content: Amend the long title so as to read: “Making further continuing appropriations for fiscal year 2020, and for other purposes.”.
Redesignate the second subsection (a) of section 1703 as subsection (b).

signature.role: Clerk of the House of Representatives.
